### [Jeremiah Chapter 46](../../../bib/kjv/jer046.htm#001.md)

[Jeremiah 46:1](../../../bib/kjv/jer046.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_001">jer 46:1</span></span>

Gentiles

A near and a far fulfilment of these prophecies against Gentile powers
are to be distinguished. In Chapter 46, the near vision is of a
Babylonian invasion of Egypt, but verses ([Jer
46:27](../../../bib/kjv/jer046.htm#027).md); ([Jer
46:28](../../../bib/kjv/jer046.htm#028).md) look forward to the judgment of
the nations.

(See Scofield) - ([Mat 25:32](../../../bib/kjv/mat025.htm#032).md),

after Armageddon ([Rev 16:14](../../../bib/kjv/rev016.htm#014).md);

(See Scofield) - ([Rev 19:17](../../../bib/kjv/rev019.htm#017).md)

and the deliverance of Israel ("Israel," ([Gen
12:2](../../../bib/kjv/gen012.htm#002).md); ([Gen
12:3](../../../bib/kjv/gen012.htm#003.md)

(See Scofield) - ([Rom 11:26](../../../bib/kjv/rom011.htm#026).md).

([Jer 50:4-7](../../../bib/kjv/jer050.htm#004).md) also looks forward to
the last days.

